<!DOCTYPE html>


<head>
    <title>@ViewBag.Title</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }



        .business-info {
            font-family: 'Cascadia Mono';
            font-size: 1.1em;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            background-color: transparent;
        }

        .about-us {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .service-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .service-list {
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        .why-choose {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }



        .container img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 40%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .image-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .image-column {
            width: 30%;
        }

            .image-column img {
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                border: 4px solid black;
            }

        h3 {
            font-size: 3.8em;
            font-family: 'Sitka Display';
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #073b6e;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            font-family: 'Cascadia Mono';
            font-size: 1.1em;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-left: 60px;
            background-color: #073b6e;
            font-family: 'Cascadia Mono';
            color: #F0e7da;
            border: 2px solid black;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: url('/Content/themes/base/images/pet_cursor.png'), pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

            .button:hover {
                background-color: black;
                color: #F0e7da;
            }
    </style>
</head>

<h3>Appointment Booking</h3>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="image-row">
            <div class="image-column">
                <img src="https://www.vetwebsites.co.za/articles/images/images/pet-owner-and-vet.png" alt="vet">
            </div>
            <div class="image-column">
                <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQaoOPZ9WqyB00DXBoxMkSMGXJ-uFqs6hWXTwn-IspdBXAGhm-Ey52GIiYpSxLExhKXa08&usqp=CAU" alt="vet">
            </div>
            <div class="image-column">
                <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcT0185U-kTzrPUEGLivxKS1q_cA7ifwK7k8wXzu437vJBy-2GeY5-erZ0TTA-dGUzBBpHQ&usqp=CAU" alt="vet">
            </div>
        </div>
        <h2>@ViewBag.Title</h2>



        <p>
            At SPCA Durban & Coast, we are dedicated to providing compassionate and comprehensive veterinary care for animals in KZN. We offer a wide range of services, including preventive care, treatment, and essential vaccinations.
        </p>


        <div class="business-info">
            <div class="service-title">Our Services:</div>
            <ul class="service-list">
                <li>
                    <strong>Treatment for Domestic and Farm Animals:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>We offer expert veterinary care for a diverse range of animals, including cats, dogs, cattle, horses, pigs, and more. Our experienced team of veterinarians is equipped to handle the unique health needs of both your household pets and valuable livestock.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Essential Vaccination Services:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Corona Vaccine:</strong> Protect your pets and farm animals from contagious coronaviruses, ensuring their safety and well-being.</li>
                        <li><strong>DPV (Distemper, Parvovirus, and Adenovirus) Vaccine:</strong> Safeguard your animals from common and potentially deadly viruses that can affect domestic and farm animals.</li>
                        <li><strong>Rabies Vaccine:</strong> Help prevent the transmission of this dangerous and fatal disease, ensuring the safety of your animals and the community.</li>
                        <li><strong>Clostridial Vaccine:</strong> Guard against a variety of clostridial diseases that can affect both domestic and farm animals, reducing the risk of illness and loss.</li>
                        <li><strong>Leptospirosis Vaccine:</strong> Protect your animals from this bacterial disease that can have severe health consequences for both pets and livestock.</li>
                        <li><strong>Brucellosis Vaccine:</strong> Ensure the health and productivity of your farm animals by vaccinating against brucellosis, a disease that can have economic and health impacts on livestock.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="business-info">
            <div class="why-choose">Why Choose the SPCA:</div>
            <p>We are committed to providing compassionate care to all animals, recognizing the special bond between pets and their owners. Our experienced veterinarians are dedicated to ensuring the health and happiness of every patient, equipped to handle diverse cases. With a focus on preventive health, we offer vaccinations and tailored care plans to keep animals thriving. Additionally, we specialize in farm animal care, promoting livestock welfare and productivity through specialized treatments and vaccinations. As a community-oriented clinic, we prioritize responsible pet ownership and support the local agricultural industry, striving to make a positive impact beyond our doors.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="business-info">
            <p>
                Contact us today to schedule an appointment or learn more about our services. Your animals' health and happiness are our top priorities.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

<div class="business-info">
    <p>
        If you already have an appointment and would like to reschedule, please click the reschedule button below:
    </p>
</div>

<div class="button-container">
    <a href="@Url.Action("Reschedule")" class="button">Reschedule Your Appointment</a>
</div>
<p></p>
<div>

    <div class="button-container">
        <a href="@Url.Action("Create")" class="button">Schedule Your Appointment</a>
    </div>
</div>
